version 0.1.2:
    - Fix the wrong EBML header in release builds (doh!)

version 0.1.1:
    - Fix the Seek Head computing mismatch for large files
    - Add a progress info during the cleaning (in 3 phases)

2010-05-04
version 0.1.0:
    - Initial public release
